Remaining gaps
Dashboard root routes — GET / and GET /dashboard are not behind auth; only /dashboard/* is. Users can load the HTML shell without a token.
Permission guard — Still regex-based and bypassable; no change.
Extension install injection — Install commands still interpolated into Dockerfile; no change.
DB migrations — No migration system.
In-memory state — Rate limiter, queue, etc. still in-memory.
Outbox race — mtime-based scan unchanged.
Container non-root — Containers still run as root.
CORS — No CORS configuration.